    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>
                <date>Feby 14th<add>?</add> 56</date>
            </p>
            <p>To <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Editor Occident”</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>
            <p>Revd &amp; Dear Sir!</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)"><add>מה חטאתי מה עויתי</add>. Wherefore have<lb/> I not
                    <sic>received</sic> the Occident for two months<lb/> already? Is it perhaps by
                forgetfulness?<lb/> Please send me the two missing numbers <date>January</date><lb/>
                &amp; <date>February</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Hoping Revd. Sir that you will<lb/> comply with the above request,
                correct<lb/> the mistake, and also that these lines<lb/> will find you enjoying the
                best<lb/> health, I remain</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">As ever</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">Yours Truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <persName role="author">Dr. B. Illowy</persName>
            </p>
            <p>My direction</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <persName role="author">Revd. Dr. B. Illowy</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>Box 2747</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(4)"><placeName>Ohio</placeName>.</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>Wherein have I sinned and transgressed</p>
        </body>
    </text>
